## Usage

### For QA Testing

1. Navigate to `/theme-preview`
2. Review all components in current theme
3. Click theme toggle in header
4. Review all components in opposite theme
5. Verify:
   - All text is readable
   - No dark-on-dark or light-on-light issues
   - Colors maintain proper contrast
   - Interactive states are visible

### For Development

1. Reference when implementing new components
2. Check which tokens to use for specific scenarios
3. Copy token names directly from the page
4. Use contrast examples as templates

### For Design Review

1. Show stakeholders all color combinations
2. Verify brand colors in both themes
3. Confirm typography scale
4. Review component styling consistency

